text:
you should start by having realistic expectations.
HRs don't usually jump at anything.

the best you can hope for is to be relevant to the position they're looking for. which means understanding what exact keywords they're looking for (see 20 open job posts for your role to know this) and have these keywords upfront and visible easily on your profile.
